    of directly calling gtk-query-immodules-2.0 in postinst and postrm.
  * Replaced hard-coded depends with ${shlibs:Depends} and ${misc:Depends}.
  * Fixed debian/dirs so it creates correct dir.
  * Do not install *.la files.
